'''飓风芭芭拉'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Barbara}}）是有纪录以来[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]位置最偏东面的[[太平洋飓风季|太平洋飓风]]，也是[[2013年太平洋飓风季|2013年太平洋飓风季]]形成的首场飓风，源自5月28日墨西哥东南方向的[[低气压|低气压区]]{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，本文所有日期均是[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]。|group="注"}}。气旋成型后缓慢朝[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]方向前进，于次日清晨达到热带风暴强度并获名“芭芭拉”。回转朝东北方向移动后，风暴于5月29日达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风标准，并以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]130公里，最低[[气压|气压]]估计为983[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.03[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度登陆[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]，成为1966年开始有可靠记录以来东太平洋盆地登陆日期第二早的飓风。接下来芭芭拉穿过[[特万特佩克地峡|特万特佩克地峡]]，最终于5月30日在[[恰帕斯马德雷山脉|恰帕斯马德雷山脉]]上空消散。

飓风芭芭拉的前身在[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]产生小到中雨，许多民宅受损，道路被淹，还有部分树木倒塌，该国有一人遇难。降水在[[危地马拉|危地马拉]]引发多起[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，迫使30人离开家园。面对风暴威胁，墨西哥发布[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]，恰帕斯州、[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]]和危地马拉开设多间避难所，学校和港口在气旋来袭期间临时关闭。据报导，当地降下倾盆大雨，许多地方停电。单恰帕斯州就有2000套房屋受损，约5万7000人流离失所。农业也受到显著影响，约有一万公顷庄稼毁于一旦。整场风暴一共导致五人死亡，直接经济损失至少有100万美元（2013年美元）。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Barbara 2013 track.png}}
[[File:Pre-Tropical_Depression_Two-E_2013-05-27_1940Z.jpg|thumbnail]]]]

5月16日，有[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸穿越大西洋，于5月24日经中美洲进入东太平洋<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Daniel P. Brown | accessdate = 2016-08-04 | date = 2013-08-06 | title = Hurricane Barbara Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP022013_Barbara.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183836/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP022013_Barbara.pdf | deadurl = no | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]这天开始监控位于[[哥斯达黎加|哥斯达黎加]]西南方向约240公里海域的扰动天气区<ref name="GTWO1">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306123430/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201305242338/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201305242338 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2013-05-24 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author = Daniel P. Brown | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201305242338/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201305242338 }}</ref>，天气系统此时正同[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]内嵌的[[季风槽|季风槽]]相互影响<ref name="TWD1">{{cite report | author = Jorge Aguirre-Echevarria | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2013-05-24 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDEP/2013/TWDEP.201305242204.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003914/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDEP/2013/TWDEP.201305242204.txt | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。虽然整体结构杂乱无章，但气象机构预计系统还是会逐渐发展<ref name="GTWO1" />。5月25日，东风波同向东移动的[[开尔文波|开尔文波]]相互影响后在尼加拉瓜西南方向形成大范围[[低气压|低气压区]]<ref name="tcr" />。刚形成的低气压区周围很快就有[[对流|对流]]组织起来，气象部门认为未来48小时内很可能会有[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]形成<ref name="GTWO2">{{cite report | author = John P. Cangialosi | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | date = 2013-05-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306122732/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201305261741/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201305261741 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201305261741/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201305261741 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref><ref name="GTWO3">{{cite report | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2013-05-27 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | author1 = John P. Cangialosi | author2 = Michael J. Brennan | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201305271141/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201305271141 | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306125020/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201305271141/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201305271141 }}</ref>。据美国国家飓风中心估算，第二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]5月28日中午12点在[[瓦哈卡州|瓦哈卡州]][[安赫尔港|安赫尔港]]（{{lang|en|Puerto ángel}}）[[罗盘方位|东南偏南]]方向约205公里洋面发展成型<ref name="tcr" />。

受[[海面温度|水温]]超过30[[摄氏温标|°C]]、[[风切变|风切变]]也很少的双重利好因素影响，刚刚形成的热带低气压迅速增强<ref name="tcr" />，深层对流聚拢成层次分明的中心<ref name="FD1">{{cite report | author1 = John P. Cangialosi | author2 = Richard J. Pasch | title = Tropical Depression Two-E Discussion Number 1 | date = 2013-05-28 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.001.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093712/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。气旋继续组织，气象机构于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}5月29日凌晨0点将热带低气压升级成热带风暴，并以“芭芭拉”（{{lang|en|Barbara}}）为其命名<ref name="FA1A">{{cite report | author1 = Robbie J. Berg | author2 = Jack L. Beven | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Intermediate Advisory Number 1A | date = 2013-05-29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.public_a.001.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305134701/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.public_a.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。风暴过后，气象部门经重新分析认定芭芭拉成为热带风暴的时间还要早六个小时<ref name="tcr" />。气旋呈现出[[风眼|眼状特征]]，风速经[[德沃夏克分析法|德沃夏克分析法]]估算已达到每小时65公里<ref name="FD2">{{cite report | author1 = Robbie J. Berg | author2 = Jack L. Beven | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Number 2 | date = 2013-05-29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002180116/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.002.shtml }}</ref>。由于[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]出现空隙，芭芭拉此时已开始回转朝东北方向前进<ref name="FD2" />。午夜时分，风暴中心的眼状特征已发展成[[中央密集云区|中央密集云区]]，周围由深层对流层层环绕<ref name="FD3">{{cite report | author1 = Todd B. Kimberlain | author2 = Daniel P. Brown | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304042033/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.003.shtml | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Number 3 | date = 2013-05-29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.003.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。芭芭拉的雨带将大部分环流包裹起来，雷达图像表明其中的风眼墙已经越来越清晰<ref name="FD3" />。此后，气旋开始加速逼近[[恰帕斯州|恰帕斯州]]海岸并继续稳步增强<ref name="FD5">{{cite report | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Christopher W. Landsea | title = Tropical Storm Barbara Discussion Number 5 | date = 2013-05-29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.005.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304093322/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.005.shtml }}</ref>。

{{lang|en|UTC}}5月29日下午18点左右，芭芭拉在瓦哈卡州[[萨利纳克鲁斯|萨利纳克鲁斯]]（{{lang|en|Salina Cruz}}）[[罗盘方位|东南偏东]]方向约105公里海域升级成飓风<ref name="PA5A">{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304230927/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.public_a.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.public_a.005.shtml | title = Hurricane Barbara Intermediate Public Advisory Number 5A | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Christopher W. Landsea | date = 2013-05-29 | deadurl = no | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-05 }}</ref>。气旋接下来达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时130公里，最低[[气压|气压]]估计为983[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]；29.03[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度<ref name="PA5A" />，然后很快就于{{lang|en|UTC}}晚上19点50分以该强度从[[托纳拉_(恰帕斯州)|托纳拉]][[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]<ref name="PAUPDATE">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.update.05292011.shtml | title = Hurricane Barbara Tropical Cyclone Update | author1 = Richard J. Pasch | author2 = Robbie J. Berg | date = 2013-05-29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304224331/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.update.05292011.shtml }}</ref>，成为1966年开始有可靠记录以来[[太平洋飓风季|东太平洋盆地]]登陆点最偏东侧、并且登陆日期第二早的飓风<ref name="FD6">{{cite report | author = Richard J. Pasch | date = 2013-05-29 | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | title = Hurricane Barbara Discussion Number 6 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070940/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.006.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.006.shtml }}</ref>。进入[[特万特佩克地峡|特万特佩克地峡]]的陆地上空后，风暴急剧减弱<ref name="FD7">{{cite report | author1 = Robbie J. Berg | author2 = Jack L. Beven | date = 2013-05-30 | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | title = Hurricane Barbara Discussion Number 7 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114011/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.007.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.007.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。随着顶层云系回暖，芭芭拉也在{{lang|en|UTC}}5月30日凌晨0点降级成热带风暴<ref name="FD7" /><ref name="PA6A">{{cite report |author1=Robbie J. Berg |author2=Jack L. Beven |title=Tropical Storm Barbara Public Advisory Number 6A |date=2013-05-30 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2016-08-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504043216/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.public_a.006.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.public_a.006.shtml |archivedate=2016-05-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。仅九小时后，气旋的下层环流已被山地扰乱，芭芭拉随即消退成热带低气压<ref name="FD8">{{cite report | author = Michael J. Brennan | date = 2013-05-30 | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | title = Hurricane Barbara Discussion Number 8 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.008.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304195505/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.discus.008.shtml }}</ref>。5月31日清晨，气旋的下层环流在墨西哥[[夸察夸尔科斯|夸察夸尔科斯]]西北偏北方向约40公里位置消散，气旋残留随后进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]<ref name="PA10">{{cite report |author=Richard J. Pasch |title=Remnants of Barbara Public Advisory Number 10 |date=2013-05-30 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |accessdate=2016-08-05 |archivedate=2016-04-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160425035925/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.public.010.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep02/ep022013.public.010.shtml |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="tcr" />。

== 防灾措施 ==
第二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压于5月28日形成后，[[墨西哥国家气象局|墨西哥国家气象局]]立即向瓦哈卡州[[查卡华泻湖国家公园|查卡华泻湖国家公园]]至恰帕斯州[[皮希希亚潘|皮希希亚潘]]（{{lang|en|Boca de Pijijiapan}}）之间的南部沿海地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]。风暴表现出升级成飓风的趋势后，上述地区又于{{lang|en|UTC}}5月29日上午10点25日进入飓风警告生效状态。<ref name="tcr" />[[坎佩切州|坎佩切州]]发布蓝色预警（最低预警级别）<ref>{{cite news | title = Emiten alerta azul en Campeche por tormenta Bárbara | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/925984.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012033241/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/925984.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-28 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。危地马拉发出“预防”警报，芭芭拉的形成和发展同对该国构成重大破坏与人员伤亡的[[飓风米奇|飓风米奇]]和[[2010年热带风暴阿加莎|热带风暴阿加莎]]类似，所以也可能引起山洪爆发<ref name="EM">{{cite news | title = Guatemala en alerta preventiva por tormenta tropical "Bárbara" en el Pacífico | newspaper = El Mundo | date = 2013-05-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012052046/http://elmundo.com.sv/guatemala-en-alerta-preventiva-por-tormenta-tropical-barbara-en-el-pacifico | url = http://elmundo.com.sv/guatemala-en-alerta-preventiva-por-tormenta-tropical-barbara-en-el-pacifico | accessdate = 2013-10-12 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。恰帕斯州西部、瓦哈卡州中部和南部接获黄色警报（中等程度威胁）<ref name="EU5">{{cite news | title = Activan alerta en cinco estados por Bárbara | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305073204/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926111.html | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926111.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-29 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>，恰帕斯州中西部、瓦哈卡州东南部和东部则进入红色警戒状态（高风险）<ref name="EU6">{{cite news | title = Bárbara se acerca a costas mexicanas ya como huracán | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131013224547/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926129.html | archivedate = 2013-10-13 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926129.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-29 }}</ref>。

多条河流沿线开有避难所<ref name="EU2">{{cite news | title = Alertan por intensas lluvias en Oaxaca | date = 2013-05-28 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/925815.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305071413/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/925815.html | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。恰帕斯州共开设有122间避难所，足以容纳30万人前来躲避<ref name="EU3">{{cite news | title = Chiapas, en alerta preventiva por posible ciclón | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/925889.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012054735/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/925889.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-28 | author = Oscar Gutierrez | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但实际前来的仅有147人。政府官员还在这些避难所中开设57个保健中心<ref name="EU4">{{cite news | title = Chiapas se prepara para enfrentar a Bárbara | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926016.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012034736/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926016.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-29 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。瓦哈卡州有20个城镇或村庄开设避难所<ref name="Yahoo!!!">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Barbara landfall in Mexico 2nd earliest | url = https://www.yahoo.com/news/hurricane-barbara-landfall-mexico-2nd-earliest-222921946.html?ref=gs | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = Yahoo News | date = 2013-05-29 | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304235937/http://news.yahoo.com/hurricane-barbara-landfall-mexico-2nd-earliest-222921946.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。恰帕斯州、瓦哈卡州和[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]的沿海居民及海上人员收到通知，建议他们谨慎行事<ref name="EU1">{{cite news | title = Alertan por ciclón frente a costas de Oaxaca | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/925963.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305072507/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/925963.html | date = 2016-08-05 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。此外，瓦哈卡州的学校停课<ref name="EU6" />，曼萨尼约海滩附近的大小船只全部抛锚靠岸，避免受到狂风巨浪的冲击，[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]也中止各项水上运动<ref name="EU8">{{cite news | title = Acapulco coloca bandera roja y cierran puertos por Bárbara | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926165.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-29 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012054927/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926165.html }}</ref>。恰帕斯州的多个港口都因风暴威胁关闭<ref name="LA">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Barbara slams into Mexico's Pacific Coast; two dead | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | archivedate = 2015-10-26 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151026153313/http://articles.latimes.com/2013/may/29/world/la-fg-wn-hurricane-barbara-mexico-pacific-coast-20130529 | date = 2013-05-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2013/may/29/world/la-fg-wn-hurricane-barbara-mexico-pacific-coast-20130529 }}</ref>。

== 影响和善后 ==

=== 中美洲 ===
芭芭拉的扰动天气前身在[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]降下小到中雨，许多民房受损，道路被淹，还有部分树木倒塌<ref name="ES">{{cite news | title = Lluvias persisten en el país por sistema de baja presión | accessdate = 2015-06-10 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.elsalvador.com/mwedh/nota/nota_completa.asp?idCat=47673&idArt=7920578 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150610201824/http://www.elsalvador.com/mwedh/nota/nota_completa.asp?idCat=47673&idArt=7920578 | newspaper = El Salvador.com | date = 2013-05-27 | author = Liseth Alues | archivedate = 2015-06-10 }}</ref>。一名44岁的女性被树砸中后伤重不治。[[阿卡胡特拉|阿卡胡特拉]]海滩附近有四幢民居受到狂风巨浪破坏，当地开有多间避难所，但仅有七人前来躲避。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sinembargo.mx/27-05-2013/634556 | title = Lluvias en el Salvador dejan un muerto y varias viviendas afectadas | date = 2013-05-27 | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | publisher = SinEmbargo | archivedate = 2013-06-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130608212138/http://www.sinembargo.mx/27-05-2013/634556 | deadurl = no }}</ref>这股扰动天气还在危地马拉引发[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，有30人因此转移到避难所<ref name="G">{{cite news | title = Dejan lluvias en el Salvador un muerto y varias viviendas afectadas | url = http://www.prensalibre.com/noticias/comunitario/Conred-declara-amarilla-depresion-tropical_0_927507485.html | archivedate = 2014-12-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141215213109/http://www.prensalibre.com/noticias/comunitario/Conred-declara-amarilla-depresion-tropical_0_927507485.html | accessdate = 2014-12-15 | newspaper = Rotavio | date = 2013-05-27 }}</ref>。

=== 墨西哥 ===
[[File:Barbara_May_29_2013_1815Z.png|thumbnail]]]]

热带风暴芭芭拉的外围雨带从5月29日清晨就开始在墨西哥多个州降下瓢泼大雨，瓦哈卡州、恰帕斯州、格雷罗州和[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]出现停电<ref>{{cite news | title = Afectará a cinco estados la tormenta tropical Bárbara | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926019.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012051113/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926019.html | deadurl = no | date = 2013-05-29 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 }}</ref><ref name="TF">{{cite news | date = 2013-05-29 | author = Notimex | url = http://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/component/content/article/47-politicasociedad/16470-tormenta-tropical-barbara-se-elevaria-a-categoria-de-huracan.html | title = Tormenta tropical Bárbara se elevaría a huracán | accessdate = 2013-10-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012025536/http://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/component/content/article/47-politicasociedad/16470-tormenta-tropical-barbara-se-elevaria-a-categoria-de-huracan.html | newspaper = El Financiero | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-10-12 }}</ref>。该国的最高降雨量达470毫米<ref>{{cite news | author = Georgina Saldierna | newspaper = La Jordana | date = 2013-06-22 | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | title = Pérdidas por $250 mil millones por sequías e inundaciones en la última década: Peña Nieto | url = http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2013/06/22/politica/009n1pol | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075117/http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2013/06/22/politica/009n1pol | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。[[奥科辛戈|奥科辛戈]]的24小时降雨量达到220.5毫米<ref name="EU3" />。风暴登陆期间袭击的大部分是未经开发的沿海泻湖，其间只有几个小渔村<ref name="Yahoo!!!" />。但是，倾盆大雨在阿卡普尔科引发严重洪灾，多条通往当地的道路被淹，还有部分高速公路受损，总体破坏程度相当可观<ref name="EU6" />。

瓦哈卡州共有四人遇难。该州近海有一名61岁的美国男子因海况恶劣溺毙，另有一名26岁的男子在试图渡河时淹死。萨利纳克鲁斯还有位60岁的男子死亡<ref name="LA" /><ref name="em-dat">{{cite report | url = http://www.emdat.be/advanced_search/index.html | title = Disaster List | work = Université Catholique de Louvain | publisher = EM-DAT: The OFDA/CRED International Disaster Database | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801161318/http://www.emdat.be/advanced_search/index.html | archivedate = 2016-08-01 | date =  }}</ref><ref name="VR">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Barbara death toll rises to three in Mexico | date = 2013-05-29 | accessdate = 2014-08-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140805060516/http://voiceofrussia.com/us/2013_05_29/Hurricane-Barbara-forms-in-Pacific-nears-Mexico-coast-US-forecasters/ | deadurl = yes | newspaper = The Voice of Russia: American edition | url = http://voicerussia.com/2013_05_29/Hurricane-Barbara-forms-in-Pacific-nears-Mexico-coast-US-forecasters/ | archivedate = 2014-08-05 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Alberto López Morales | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-29 | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | title = Oleaje de huracán Bárbara deja un muerto en Oaxaca | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012033024/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926185.html | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926185.html }}</ref>。此外，[[圣佩德罗塔帕纳特佩克|塔帕纳特佩克]]（{{lang|en|Tapanatepec}}）有14名渔夫失踪<ref name="LA" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Barbara floods Mexico's southern Pacific coast, kills two | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | author = Jose Cortes | agency = [[路透社|Ruters]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055917/http://worldnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/05/30/18600922-hurricane-barbara-floods-mexicos-southern-pacific-coast-kills-two?lite | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date = 2013-05-29 | deadurl = no | url = http://worldnews.nbcnews.com/_news/2013/05/30/18600922-hurricane-barbara-floods-mexicos-southern-pacific-coast-kills-two?lite }}</ref>，其中两人很快生还<ref name="VR" />，另有八人在气旋过后数天内获救<ref name="EO">{{cite news | title = Declaran emergencia al sur de México por daños de huracán Bárbara | date = 2013-05-31 | newspaper = El Universo | url = http://www.eluniverso.com/noticias/2013/05/31/nota/973481/declaran-emergencia-sur-mexico-danos-huracan-barbara | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310084556/http://www.eluniverso.com/noticias/2013/05/31/nota/973481/declaran-emergencia-sur-mexico-danos-huracan-barbara }}</ref>。余下的四人始终下落不明，推定其中一人已经死亡<ref name="em-dat" />。[[托纳拉_(恰帕斯州)|托纳拉]]和[[阿里亚加|阿里亚加]]（{{lang|en|Arriaga}}）是飓风灾情最严重的地区，数十棵树木、电线杆，以及广告牌和屋顶因狂风受损，许多餐厅被大浪摧毁，多户民宅被淹或被毁，导致许多人无家可归<ref>{{cite news | title = Tonalá y Arriaga, los más afectados por Bárbara | date = 2013-05-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012044747/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926371.html | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926371.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2013-10-12 }}</ref>。不过，恰帕斯州其他地区的破坏程度很轻<ref name="EU9">{{cite news | title = Daños menores en Chiapas tras paso de 'Bárbara' | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926481.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-30 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012055517/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926481.html }}</ref>。该州共有50人撤离，约2000套民房受损<ref name="EU10">{{cite news | title = Hallan a salvo a pescadores dados por perdidos en Oaxaca | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926483.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012022352/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926483.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-30 | author = Lopez Morals | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。墨西哥全国共有5万7000人流离失所，一万公顷农作物毁于一旦<ref name="EU17">{{cite news | title = Bárbara dejó más de 57 mil damnificados | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/927804.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305194058/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/927804.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-06-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，其中[[芒果|芒果]]作物约有3500公顷，估计损失的芒果有2万2751.88吨<ref>{{cite news | author = Octavio Vélez Ascencio | newspaper = Noticias Net | date = 2013-06-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150610230918/http://www.noticiasnet.mx/portal/oaxaca/156567-quiebra-barbara-cultivos-mango | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | title = Quiebra Bárbara cultivos de mango | archivedate = 2015-06-10 | deadurl = no | url = http://old.nvinoticias.com/oaxaca/156567-quiebra-barbara-cultivos-mango }}</ref>，损失数额约为1000至1500万[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（相当于同年的75至110万美元）<ref>{{cite news | author = Octavio Vélez | newspaper = Noticias Net | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191456/http://www.noticiasnet.mx/portal/oaxaca/general/agropecuarias/154758-pierden-mangueros-10-dmp-danos-causados-barbara | date = 2013-06-04 | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | title = Pierden los mangueros 10 dmp por daños causados por "Bárbara" | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://old.nvinoticias.com/oaxaca/general/agropecuarias/154758-pierden-mangueros-10-dmp-danos-causados-barbara }}</ref>。

芭芭拉令墨西哥1万9000人受灾，风暴过后该国开设16间医疗中心，共127名医生和318名护士向受灾最严重的地区提供医疗服务<ref name="EU11">{{cite news | title = Bárbara deja 19 mil  damnificados: Velasco | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150610215338/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926769.html | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926769.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2015-06-10 | date = 2013-05-31 }}</ref>。恰帕斯州和瓦哈卡州分别有36和五个[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]]进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Declaran en emergencia 32 municipios de Chiapas | date = 2013-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131014034539/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/90909.html | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/90909.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | archivedate = 2013-10-14 }}</ref><ref name="EU12">{{cite news | title = Declaran emergencia en cinco municipios de Oaxaca | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150610212625/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926724.html | archivedate = 2015-06-10 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/926724.html | accessdate = 2016-08-05 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2013-05-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
